<h3>Start your application</h3>

<p>Each organisation can only make one application to scrap up to three vehicles. You can't add or remove vehicles to your application once you've submitted it.</p>

<p>To start your application you'll need to sign in to or create a London Road User Charging (LRUC) account. On your account landing page look for the 'Scrappage scheme' link.</p>
